        <briefdescription>
<para>Header checksum in octal ASCII. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Calculated by treating these 8 bytes as ASCII spaces, summing all 512 bytes of the header as unsigned bytes, and storing the result as an octal string followed by a null and a space. Binary encoding is strictly forbidden here. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
        </detaileddescription>
        <inbodydescription>
